{"tid":1505132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[歷史重温] 一哥讚展現無比勇氣　 旺角騷亂　開槍警獲頒花雞繩","createTime":"2019-08-25T12:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T13:21:37.000Z","uid":15010,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8341b96e30bfda764fbf805c3c2aba47e66db583","tid":1505132,"uid":15010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:55:48.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】今年農曆年初二凌晨發生的旺角騷亂，造成過百警務人員受傷，警隊論功行賞，近百名來自15個警隊單位的警務人員昨<span style=\"color: red;\">獲警務處處長盧偉聰正式嘉許</span>，其中4名警務人員獲頒俗稱「花雞繩」的警務處處長嘉許，包括當晚向天連開兩槍示警、綽號「高威」的西九龍交通部警員黃慶威。多個關注團體及立法會議員批評警方嘉許開槍示警人員不恰當，只會加劇警民矛盾。<br />\n記者：謝明明<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20160811/19731890\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20160811%2F19731890&d=06o7JzqVhDqA6Aam%2BaIp8xphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=604785c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20160811%2F19731890&h=54012ed3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20160811/19731890</a>"},{"pid":"c6ddcee9e2546a5aa380128815f556fa7c8ea162","tid":1505132,"uid":15010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:59:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7c7e75ec5b9dac79a97c07a1e785150d66ee425","tid":1505132,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:59:35.000Z","msg":"殺人放火金腰帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24bff05a7f265139a8832893f78ea4a3443cbd20","tid":1505132,"uid":202917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8341b96e30bfda764fbf805c3c2aba47e66db583","tid":1505132,"uid":15010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"